        "content": "<p>Ikšķilē top Rimi - pirms pāris dienām jau izskatījās, ka nav vairs daudz palicis.<br>\nJa nu kāds tur garām dodas, varbūt vērts paskatīties, vai nevar jau kaut ko vairāk iezīmēt.<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=17/56.832036/24.491336\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=17/56.832036/24.491336</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=17/56.832036/24.491336\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d656430323866393034363832323461323732393631633338306563656530636662373362383034386233346634623462323034623766306431303937383735642e706e67&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=17/56.832036/24.491336\" title=\"OpenStreetMap\">OpenStreetMap</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.</div></div></div>",
